comments: Gafford (WAS) initiates contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm during his upward motion, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) moves in the same direction as Kispert (WAS) with a hand resting on Kispert's body and marginal contact occurs before the defensive switch on the perimeter.
Poole (WAS) lifts his pivot foot before his release at the start of his dribble.
Poole (WAS) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Jones (WAS) lunges forward into Maxey (PHI) and delivers body contact, which affects Maxey's SQBR.
Poole (WAS) clamps and holds Embiid's (PHI) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Harris (PHI) and Kuzma (WAS) briefly engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Kuzma (WAS) and Embiid (PHI) mutually engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs as they jostle for position off-ball.
Avdija (WAS) comes across and initiates contact with Embiid's (PHI) wrists, which affects his play at the basket.
Kispert (WAS) initiates contact with Embiid's (PHI) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Kispert (WAS) firms up on his left foot in Embiid's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Kuzma (WAS) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Maxey (PHI) brings his arm toward Jones' (WAS) path and marginal contact occurs during Jones' drive.
Embiid (PHI) and Poole (WAS) begin to position themselves for potential rebounding position and incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs, which causes Poole to lose his balance.
Kuzma (WAS) commits a take foul on Melton (PHI).
Poole (WAS) commits a take foul on Melton (PHI).
